  <h1>Structural Calculation Report</h1>
  <div class="subtitle">Single-span portal frame — SANS 10162-1:2011 / SANS 10160 series</div>
  <div class="meta">
    Generated: {{ generated_at }} (UTC)<br>
    Frame: {{ geom.span_m }} m span &times; {{ geom.eaves_height_m }} m eaves &times; {{ geom.roof_pitch_deg }}&deg; pitch &times; {{ geom.bay_spacing_m }} m bay<br>
    Report fingerprint: <span style="font-family: monospace; font-size:8pt;">{{ report_fingerprint[:16] }}&hellip;</span>
  </div>
