    <td>Elastic M<sub>cr</sub></td>
    <td>L<sub>u</sub> = {{ "%.0f"|format(mw.LTB_mm) }} mm, &omega;<sub>2</sub> = 1.00</td>
    <td class="num">{{ "%.2f"|format(mw.mcr_knm) }} kN&middot;m</td>
    <td style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size:7.5pt;">cl. 13.6</td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="font-weight:bold; background:#EFF6FF;">
    <td>Moment M<sub>r</sub> (LTB)</td>
    <td>Class {{ mw.section_class }}, Z<sub>pl</sub> = {{ "{:,.0f}".format(mw.zpl_mm3) }} mm&sup3;</td>
    <td class="num">{{ "%.2f"|format(mw.mr_knm) }} kN&middot;m</td>
    <td style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size:7.5pt;">cl. 13.5/13.6</td>
  </tr>
</table>
{% endfor %}

<!-- ================================================================ -->
<!-- 9. AUDIT METADATA (PRD FR-20)                                    -->
<!-- ================================================================ -->
<h2>12. Audit Metadata</h2>
<p style="font-size:8.5pt; color:var(--color-muted); margin-bottom:6pt;">
  FR-20: Reports record the code-rule version, complete input spec, and a timestamp
  so that results can be reproduced exactly from the same inputs.
</p>

<h3>Report Identity</h3>
<table>
  <tr><th style="width:40%">Field</th><th>Value</th></tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Generated at (UTC)</td>
    <td style="font-family: var(--font-mono)">{{ generated_at }}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Report fingerprint (SHA-256)</td>
    <td style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size:8pt; word-break:break-all;">{{ report_fingerprint }}</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<div class="box" style="font-size:8.5pt;">
  The fingerprint is SHA-256(canonical JSON of DesignResult). Reproduce this report by
  supplying the identical input spec and kernel version — the fingerprint will match.
</div>

<h3>Complete Input Specification</h3>
<table>
  <tr><th colspan="2" style="background:var(--color-brand-light);">Geometry</th></tr>
  <tr><td style="width:45%">Span</td>                <td class="num">{{ geom.span_m }} m</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Eaves height</td>            <td class="num">{{ geom.eaves_height_m }} m</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Roof pitch</td>              <td class="num">{{ geom.roof_pitch_deg }}&deg;</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Bay spacing</td>             <td class="num">{{ geom.bay_spacing_m }} m</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Number of bays</td>          <td class="num">{{ geom.number_of_bays }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Apex height (computed)</td>  <td class="num">{{ "%.3f"|format(geom.apex_height_m) }} m</td></tr>

  <tr><th colspan="2" style="background:var(--color-brand-light);">Dead Loads (characteristic)</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Roof area load</td>          <td class="num">{{ dead.roof_kpa }} kPa</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Services load</td>           <td class="num">{{ dead.services_kpa }} kPa</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Wall cladding load</td>      <td class="num">{{ dead.wall_cladding_kpa }} kPa</td></tr>

  <tr><th colspan="2" style="background:var(--color-brand-light);">Wind</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Basic wind speed</td>        <td class="num">{{ wind.basic_wind_speed_ms }} m/s</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Terrain category</td>        <td>{{ wind.terrain_category.value }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Site altitude</td>           <td class="num">{{ wind.site_altitude_m }} m</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Dominant opening</td>        <td>{{ "Yes" if wind.has_dominant_opening else "No" }}</td></tr>

  <tr><th colspan="2" style="background:var(--color-brand-light);">Materials and Fixity</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Steel grade</td>             <td>{{ steel_grade }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Base fixity</td>             <td>{{ base_fixity }}</td></tr>

  <tr><th colspan="2" style="background:var(--color-brand-light);">Restraints (LTB unbraced lengths)</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Rafter restraint spacing</td>
      <td class="num">{% if restraints_rafter_m %}{{ restraints_rafter_m }} m{% else %}Unrestrained (full rafter half-length){% endif %}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Column restraint spacing</td>
      <td class="num">{% if restraints_column_m %}{{ restraints_column_m }} m{% else %}Unrestrained (full eaves height){% endif %}</td></tr>
</table>

<!-- ================================================================ -->
<!-- ENGINEER REVIEW & SIGN-OFF                                        -->
<!-- ================================================================ -->
<div class="signoff">
  <h3>Engineer review &amp; sign-off</h3>
  {% if stamp %}
  <div class="stamp-mark">
    <div class="stamp-title">&#10003; Digitally stamped — registered engineer</div>
    <div class="stamp-name">{{ stamp.engineer_name }}</div>
    <div class="stamp-meta">
      ECSA registration no. {{ stamp.ecsa_reg_no }}<br>
      Stamped: {{ stamp.stamped_at }} (UTC)<br>
      Bound to report fingerprint:
      <span style="font-family: monospace; font-size:8pt;">{{ stamp.fingerprint }}</span>
    </div>
    <p class="note" style="margin-top:6pt;">
      The named professional, registered with the Engineering Council of South Africa (ECSA), has
      independently reviewed and verified this design — including every item flagged PROVISIONAL or
      out of scope — and accepts professional responsibility for it. This digital stamp is bound to
      the report fingerprint above; any change to the design changes the fingerprint and voids the stamp.
    </p>
  </div>
  {% else %}
  <p class="note">
    By signing below, the reviewing professional confirms they are registered with the Engineering
    Council of South Africa (ECSA), have independently reviewed and verified this design — including
    every item flagged PROVISIONAL or out of scope — and accept professional responsibility for it.
  </p>
  <table class="signoff-table">
    <tr>
      <td><div class="label">Reviewed &amp; verified by</div><div class="line">{% if doc and doc.engineer_name %}{{ doc.engineer_name }}{% endif %}</div></td>
      <td><div class="label">ECSA registration no.</div><div class="line">{% if doc and doc.engineer_reg_no %}{{ doc.engineer_reg_no }}{% endif %}</div></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><div class="label">Signature</div><div class="line"></div></td>
      <td><div class="label">Date</div><div class="line"></div></td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  {% endif %}
</div>

<!-- ================================================================ -->
<!-- PROVENANCE FOOTER                                                 -->
<!-- ================================================================ -->
<div class="provenance">
  All engineering values computed by <strong>TorenOne deterministic kernel</strong>
  — not by an AI language model. This report is machine-generated; a registered
  structural engineer must review and accept responsibility for all design decisions
  before these calculations are used in construction.
  Generated: {{ generated_at }} (UTC) &middot; Fingerprint: {{ report_fingerprint[:16] }}&hellip;
</div>

</body>
</html>
